<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : meir3555_IntT</h1>
<div><p>Suita de teste pentru integrarea top-down a clasei OrderService.<br />
Include 3 cazuri de testare: Step 1 - unit testing S, Step 2 - integrare partiala, Step 3 - integrare cu repository real.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc30747"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P234-65: meir3555_IntT_Step1_Unit_OrderService_GetAllOrders&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
